00:54.087 --> 00:56.487
<i>Sometimes pain becomes</i>
<i>such a huge part of your life</i>

00:56.556 --> 00:58.319
<i>that you expect it to always be there</i>

00:59.559 --> 01:02.289
<i>because you can't remember</i>
<i>a time in your life when it wasn't.</i>

01:03.630 --> 01:06.531
<i>But then, one day,</i>
<i>you feel something else,</i>

01:06.599 --> 01:10.365
<i>something that feels wrong,</i>
<i>but only because it's so unfamiliar,</i>

01:11.171 --> 01:14.607
<i>and, in that moment,</i>
<i>you realize you're happy.</i>

01:15.375 --> 01:16.842
Hey, blondie.

01:18.000 --> 01:24.074
Advertise your product or brand here
contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

01:27.120 --> 01:28.678
