02:38.992 --> 02:40.584
Oh, have you guys met Chase?

02:41.561 --> 02:44.325
He's our newest member.
He just transferred from Westerberg.

02:46.866 --> 02:49.357
Hi. Brooke Davis, Clean Teen.

03:52.665 --> 03:56.123
- Oh, God, sorry.
- It's all right.

04:06.079 --> 04:08.445
