07:00.653 --> 07:01.813
Look at this one.

07:05.391 --> 07:09.088
Think about it. Think about it.
Think about it. Think about it.

07:11.664 --> 07:12.653
Here we go.

07:12.832 --> 07:14.663
Thank you. Did you remember the cheese?

07:14.734 --> 07:16.634
- Right on top.
- Karen!

07:20.740 --> 07:24.335
I used to have one of those.
I tried to put it to sleep.

07:26.546 --> 07:28.013
Looks like you got yours neutered.

07:28.614 --> 07:29.638
Good morning, Deb.

07:29.916 --> 07:32.043
What are you here for? Target practice?

07:32.118 --> 07:34.416
You know, for a smart woman
you're being really stupid

07:34.487 --> 07:36.011
letting Dan into your life.

07:36.088 --> 07:37.316
The one who abandoned you

07:37.390 --> 07:39.517
