and left Lucas fatherless.

07:39.592 --> 07:42.083
The one who treated Keith horribly
his whole life.

07:42.161 --> 07:43.685
You remember Keith, don't you?

07:43.763 --> 07:46.664
- The man whose baby you're carrying?
- That's enough.

07:46.966 --> 07:50.163
He would roll over in his grave
if he could see the two of you together!

07:55.675 --> 07:57.643
Maybe my being here is a bad idea.

08:02.448 --> 08:04.541
<i>This whole thing was a bad idea.</i>

08:04.650 --> 08:06.345
I should have never cheated on the test.

08:12.658 --> 08:15.252
Or maybe it was the best idea ever!

08:16.229 --> 08:18.197
