08:29.308 --> 08:31.037
Sure, anytime.

08:34.780 --> 08:37.179
Check me out. I'm a smart virgin.

08:37.884 --> 08:40.010
Great, you're the new Mouth.

08:43.389 --> 08:49.055
Okay, look, just so you know,
<i>Kid A</i> goes under "R" for Radiohead.

08:49.128 --> 08:50.652
