08:55.234 --> 08:58.135
Yes. Alphabetized by genre and sub-genre.

08:59.305 --> 09:00.533
Okay, music genius,

09:01.574 --> 09:03.872
can you tell me who
sings this song on the radio right now?

09:04.544 --> 09:06.239
Watch and be amazed.

09:18.724 --> 09:20.055
