09:20.927 --> 09:23.259
- That's pretty awesome.
- I know.

09:24.697 --> 09:26.392
Kind of like your smile.

09:26.899 --> 09:28.764
- No, happy looks good on you.
- Yeah?

09:30.036 --> 09:32.095
I feel like I'm living in an Air Supply song.

09:32.171 --> 09:36.005
Well, you know, if we're going to go '80s,
I'm more of a Van Halen fan.

09:36.676 --> 09:40.612
No, it's just...
Everything's better now, you know?

09:41.013 --> 09:45.313
Pinks are pinker and blues are bluer,

09:45.384 --> 09:48.012
and even my favorite foods taste yummier.

09:48.087 --> 09:50.248
- Yummier?
- Yummier.

09:50.323 --> 09:52.257
What's your favorite food?

09:52.325 --> 09:53.383
Chocolate chip cookies.

09:53.459 --> 09:56.826
I'll tell you what,
they probably taste so much better.

09:57.263 --> 10:00.391
Well, if anyone can make
a chocolate chip cookie taste better,

10:00.466 --> 10:01.455
I'm sure it's you.

10:01.534 --> 10:04.264
Oh, see? You're so feeling the love.

10:04.337 --> 10:06.669
Oh, sure. Anything for a cookie.

10:09.075 --> 10:10.542
Come with me.

10:14.380 --> 10:17.315
So, you know,
if we're both feeling the love,

10:18.351 --> 10:20.046
what are we doing in a cemetery?

10:20.953 --> 10:22.352
There's somebody I want you to meet.

10:22.888 --> 10:26.255
Hi, Mom. It's me.

10:27.827 --> 10:31.263
So this is Lucas,
the boy I've been telling you about.

10:32.164 --> 10:34.962
Look what he's done. He's got me smiling.

10:35.668 --> 10:36.862
Can you believe it?

10:38.270 --> 10:39.567
Hey, Mrs. Sawyer.

10:40.806 --> 10:42.171
I just want you to know that

10:43.376 --> 10:44.900
Peyton's the best thing I have in my life.

10:47.146 --> 10:48.977
I wouldn't even be here if it wasn't for her.

10:50.583 --> 10:51.572
Likewise.

10:59.692 --> 11:02.126
- Can I have a sec?
- Yeah.

11:11.003 --> 11:12.265
So, what do you think?

11:12.905 --> 11:14.099
He's cute, huh?

11:15.041 --> 11:16.030
Hey, Keith.

11:24.650 --> 11:26.174
Open your eyes, Luke.

11:41.467 --> 11:43.799
I still don't believe
that Jimmy killed you, Keith.

11:43.869 --> 11:44.893
<i>You were here that day.</i>

11:44.970 --> 11:46.028
<i>What did you see?</i>

11:46.639 --> 11:47.799
