somewhere in this world that fit me,

12:58.878 --> 13:02.211
we don't even have any money
for it anyway. It's okay.

13:02.281 --> 13:05.614
You know what? It's okay.

13:05.718 --> 13:10.587
I'll just... I'll go and I'll be pregnant
and gimpy and, you know,

13:10.656 --> 13:11.918
