13:11.991 --> 13:15.085
Hey.
Hey, you'll look great in anything, okay?

13:15.728 --> 13:17.252
It's all right.

13:18.164 --> 13:20.189
Except maybe that dress.

13:24.537 --> 13:26.061
Haley...

13:32.778 --> 13:34.405
Just how naked do we have to get?

13:36.515 --> 13:39.143
See? I knew you would come around.

13:39.685 --> 13:41.448
Don't worry, man.
We're gonna win this thing.

13:41.520 --> 13:44.114
I don't know, man,
you haven't seen me dance. I'm terrible.

13:44.190 --> 13:46.658
Man, you'll be fine.
We got the best choreographer in town.

13:46.725 --> 13:48.886
Hey, Nate. Skills said you'd come around.

13:50.529 --> 13:54.295
